## Index cards

### Schema parser

|                     |                                                                                                                                                                         |
| ------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **When**            | Edges wrong, cardinality wrong, reference targets missing, coverage/source tabs                                                                                         |
| **Read**            | `lib/dev/parse-ontology.ts`, `lib/dev/types.ts`                                                                                                                         |
| **Source of truth** | `.cursor/rules/ontology.mdc` (YAML block)                                                                                                                               |
| **Key idea**        | `buildRelationships()` dedupes type-pairs; `extractReferenceTargetsFromRawYaml` must use **line index** (not `indexOf`) when duplicate `type: reference` comments exist |
| **Gotcha**          | Missing reciprocal `referenceTarget` â†’ `targetCardinality` defaults to `one`                                                                                            |

